Comment: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书记 2-2 高田千惠 85%
Comment: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同上
Comment: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,书记 2-1 北川翔 83%
Comment: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同上
