Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊 那家伙也说过她在一年级里很有人气的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是优秀的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为主人 我可以允许暂时由森大人来使役她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:38.17,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(806,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样很可能会渐渐变成小森大人的侍从了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:45.34,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(793,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 现在我只要请她帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然 请让凸守来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森… 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷学姐要成为学生会会长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将这所学校带往《暗黑圣典》中记载的受到精灵守护的香格里拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:08.49,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,660)}<Mabinogion>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊啊啊这件事要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身份会被大家知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 能请你从今天开始帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是学生会会长候选人 丹生谷森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让各位的学习生活更加美好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是学生会会长候选人 一色诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就完成…的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 绘画也很出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.86,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H403C3D&\3c&HC1C3C1&\pos(839,112)}为\N大\N家\N的\N明\N天{\c&H3A31AD&}\N努\N力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\pos(349,465)}给\N老\N子\N跟\N上\N！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷学姐的海报 感觉很神圣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小凸的偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 多亏了小凸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在一年级获得这么高的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 支持率70%的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩什么时候开始这么要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才… 才没有 我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守跟森夏大人早在300年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.43,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(548,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被神圣绸缎系在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 森夏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.51,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 啊…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守 今天月色泛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,召唤魔界兽一起探险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守今天跟森夏大人有非常重要的会议要开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.91,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(506,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是… 那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富㭴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我跟你一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要先写完作业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么 勇太会说和圣调理人一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.94,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(765,660)}<Priestesse>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你们暗中勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.36,註釋,,0000,0000,0000,,日语「内通」有私通之意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 森夏大人的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.28,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(592,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来跟凡人一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森夏大人的身份对家人也是保密的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.87,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(369,660)}<Mori Summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直忍受着这样的孤独吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢… 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 关于同场演讲会的应援演讲稿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我已经写到一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这饼干的形状 莫非是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请… 请问怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她总是说一些令人生气的话而没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她或许是一个非常纯真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为他人着想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.62,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,660)}<Mori summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活了400年之久的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在精灵的细语之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你献上教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森夏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.97,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(594,660)}<Mori summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于… 终于遇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的烦恼是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小凸 照相就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一张 请让我留一张就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小凸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这一张 只要这一张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森夏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.54,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(599,660)}<Mori summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人… 主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显身吧 魔界兽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,揭示吾所寻求之物的沉睡之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷那家伙真的有可能当选啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会长… 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七宫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是魔界兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 退后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 洗澡水平备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就要朝着顶峰迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是男人就要胸怀大志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想君临于大家顶点的一色诚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色 你这是要走向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到你了 紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘记原稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 原稿也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 我为了向凡人宣传森夏大人正确的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.98,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,<Mori summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从而进行意识改革
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还对前些天的演讲稿作了修改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使其更加具有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面有请担任丹生谷森夏同学应援演讲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年级学生 凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是担任丹生谷应援演讲的凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我将为诸君传达森夏大人温暖而又意味深长的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:12.77,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,660)}<Mori summer>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一章第三节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界的构造便是爱的节理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这400年来我一直注视着人们心中的暗流涌动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争 仇恨 争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类为什么要让这些事情不断发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精灵永远在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传颂着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 会心一击？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天丹生没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,险些被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么肯定吗喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《暗黑圣典》是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.08,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,660)}<Mabinogion>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对书中的话语感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是冒牌货的确凿证据
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然凸守的主人只有您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了啊 冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 果然全都是《暗黑圣典》的错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.40,Default-2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(766,660)}<Mabinogion>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货别在那里大言不惭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会给冒牌货呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了我叫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是这样比较令人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快给我交出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
